<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Parental Consent Required</h1>

  <p>Dear Parent/Guardian,</p>

  <p>Your child, <%= @user.email %>, has requested to participate in our organization-based access control system.</p>

  <p><strong>Child's Information:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <%= @user.email %></li>
    <li>Age: <%= @user.age %> years old</li>
    <li>Date of Birth: <%= @user.date_of_birth.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  </ul>

  <% if @organization %>
    <p><strong>Organization:</strong> <%= @organization.name %></p>
    <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @organization.description %></p>
  <% end %>

  <p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your child will be able to join organization and participate in age-appropriate activities</li>
    <li>All content will be filtered based on their age</li>
    <li>You can revoke consent at any time</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>To approve consent:</strong></p>
  <p>
    <%= link_to "APPROVE CONSENT", approve_parental_consent_url(@parental_consent.id, token: @parental_consent.generate_approval_token),
        style: "background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
  </p>

  <p><strong>To deny consent:</strong></p>
  <p>
    <%= link_to "DENY CONSENT", deny_parental_consent_url(@parental_consent.id, token: @parental_consent.generate_denial_token),
        style: "background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
  </p>
  <p>If you have any questions, please contact us.</p>

  <p>Thank you,<br>
  OrgSpace Team</p>
</body>
</html>
